<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2016-02-04</DATELINE><TITLE>A windfall for US biomedical science</TITLE><BODY>In December, the US government approved a $2 billion increase in the budget of the US National Institutes of Health (NIH) for the 2016 fiscal year. With that increase comes relief, optimism and the pressure to spend wisely.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>